{{en-noun|species|pl2qual=rare, nonstandard|+}}

# [[type|Type]] or [[kind]]. {{q|Compare {{m|en|race}}.}}
#: {{ux|en|the male '''species'''}}
#: {{ux|en|a new '''species''' of war}}
